&lt;li&gt;BS or MS in Computer Science, a related field, equivalent industry experience, or equivalent educational experience.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Legally eligible to work in India on an ongoing basis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in English is required&lt;/li&gt;
